00:26:28,746 --> 00:26:30,467
So how many of you have had this experience?

484
00:26:30,547 --> 00:26:34,110
You're writing some system, you're coding something, you have to dig into some system,

485
00:26:34,170 --> 00:26:35,712
maybe you haven't seen that system before.

486
00:26:36,252 --> 00:26:40,096
And your immediate reaction as soon as you look into the code for this other system is

487
00:26:40,116 --> 00:26:40,816
something like this.

488
00:26:43,098 --> 00:26:43,739
Maybe it's this.

489
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:47,502
Or what I tend to see more often is something like this.

490
00:26:49,690 --> 00:26:51,172
We've all had this experience, right?

